  + sr [Danilo Šegan]
  + sv [Christian Rose]

GNOME-Mud 0.10.3 (11/11/2003)

- Wizard and profilenames are now escape and can contain "space" and
  other characters. (Bug #117241) [Robin]
- Fix segfaults in Connection Wizard. (Bug #117242) [Robin]
- New translations:
